from distutils.core import setup

VERSION = "1.5.3"

    name = "PySocks",

    url = "https://github.com/Anorov/PySocks",
    license = "BSD",
    author = "Anorov",
    author_email = "anorov.vorona@gmail.com",
    keywords = ["socks", "proxy"],
